org.apache.flink.formats.avro

类 AvroRowDeserializationSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.serialization.AbstractDeserializationSchema<Row>
      • org.apache.flink.formats.avro.AvroRowDeserializationSchema
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, DeserializationSchema<Row>, ResultTypeQueryable<Row>

    public class AvroRowDeserializationSchema
extends AbstractDeserializationSchema<Row>
    Deserialization schema from Avro bytes over SpecificRecord to Row.

    Deserializes the byte[] messages into (nested) Flink Rows. Utf8 is converted to regular Java Strings.
